go to the movies every day...

100
00:08:18,257 --> 00:08:19,884
...even though l'd love to.

101
00:08:20,092 --> 00:08:22,060
While we wait for a cab...

102
00:08:22,261 --> 00:08:24,821
...l'll give you
your lesson for today.

103
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:26,554
Your lesson is this:

104
00:08:26,765 --> 00:08:29,495
Don't listen to what
your teachers say.

105
00:08:29,701 --> 00:08:31,794
Just see what they look like.

106
00:08:32,004 --> 00:08:35,235
Then you'll know what life
will really be like.

107
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:38,637
You heard it here first.
l see a cab. lf we run...

108
00:08:38,844 --> 00:08:42,569
...we can kick the crutch
from that old lady and get it.

109
00:08:44,604 --> 00:08:47,300
-l'm back!
-Where were you?

110
00:08:47,507 --> 00:08:51,603
-Just out and around.
-Took your niece to a movie again.

111
00:08:51,811 --> 00:08:54,974
l'm crazy about that kid.
She's just great.

112
00:08:55,181 --> 00:08:58,878
My brother's in town.
He asked us to a dinner party.

113
00:08:59,085 --> 00:09:02,452
-Jesus.
-Please. You gonna make another scene?

114
00:09:02,655 --> 00:09:06,853
-l didn't do that last time.
