115
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:12,327
l don't resent him. He's a pompous ass.
You don't see it since you love him.

116
00:09:12,532 --> 00:09:14,193
-What did you say?
-Nothing.

117
00:09:14,401 --> 00:09:16,892
You did. You're running down Lester.

118
00:09:17,103 --> 00:09:20,561
-l like your brother Ben.
