Out there is such
a Mickey Mouse environment.

145
00:10:51,998 --> 00:10:53,397
The reason l'm here--

146
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:57,263
-Hello, Lester.
-l wanna talk to you. Don't go away.

147
00:10:57,470 --> 00:11:00,598
A bunch of us are getting together...

148
00:11:00,807 --> 00:11:03,537
...to build a studio here in the city.

149
00:11:03,743 --> 00:11:07,042
ln fact-- l'm sorry,
just give me one second.

150
00:11:07,247 --> 00:11:08,680
ldea for series:

151
00:11:08,882 --> 00:11:12,215
A high-profile builder,
