154
00:11:18,591 --> 00:11:22,118
Ben, Carol, come here.
Hi, kid. Nice to see you.

155
00:11:23,029 --> 00:11:24,690
-Hi, honey.
-Hi, sweetheart.

156
00:11:24,898 --> 00:11:27,992
-Hi, Cliff.
-How you doing? How are your eyes?

157
00:11:28,201 --> 00:11:30,999
Not so good. lt's not so optimistic.

158
00:11:31,204 --> 00:11:33,468
l've been seeing Dr. Rosenthal.

159
00:11:33,673 --> 00:11:36,642
Lester, don't you want
to talk to Clifford?

160
00:11:36,843 --> 00:11:39,437
Oh, yeah. Step into my office.

161
00:11:40,847 --> 00:11:44,078
-Hi, l'm Lisa.
